# Sensitive Lab Information - NEVER UPLOAD THESE
# ==============================================================================
# GitHub Repository Protection Filter Matrix (.gitignore)
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. SENSITIVE CREDENTIALS & LOCAL CONFIGURATIONS (CRITICAL SECURITY)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Blocks the local file where your real passwords and webhook URLs live
.env
*.env
*.secrets
secrets.json
auth_tokens.txt

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. LOCAL TRANSACTION LOGS & SIEM TELEMETRY DATA
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prevents raw alert logs or incident tracking files from leaking online
*.log
shuffle.log
servicenow.log

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. PYTHON ENVIRONMENT & COMPILED ARTIFACTS
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Keeps your repository clean of automated python cache folders
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Local Python Virtual Environments
.venv/
venv/
env/

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. OPERATING SYSTEM TEMPORARY FILES
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.tmp